form7.com/captcha/','Generate form-tags for a CAPTCHA image and corresponding response input field. For more details, see %s.'=>'为人机识别系统图像和相应的响应输入字段创建form标签。 有关更多详细信息，请参阅 %s。','To use CAPTCHA, you first need to install and activate %s plugin.'=>'要使用人机识别系统，您首先需要安装和激活 %s 插件。','CAPTCHA'=>'CAPTCHA','Your entered code is incorrect.'=>'您输入的验证码不正确。','The code that sender entered does not match the CAPTCHA'=>'发件人输入的验证码和CAPTCHA的不匹配','Insert Tag'=>'插入标签','Class attribute'=>'样式属性','Id attribute'=>'ID属性','Options'=>'可选项','Name'=>'名字','Acceptance checkbox'=>'接受复选框','https://contactform7.com/acceptance-checkbox/'=>'https://contactform7.com/acceptance-checkbox/','Generate a form-tag for an acceptance checkbox. For more details, see %s.'=>'为复选框创建form标签。 有关更多详细信息，请参阅 %s。','acceptance'=>'接受','<code>%1$s</code> property of a <code>WPCF7_ContactForm</code> object is <strong>no longer accessible</strong>. Use <code>%2$s</code> method instead.'=>'<code>WPCF7_ContactForm</code> 对象的<code>%1$s</code>属性 <strong>已经废除</strong>。请使用<code>%2$s</code>代替。','Untitled'=>'没有标题','Contact Form'=>'联系表单','There is a field with input that is shorter than the minimum allowed length'=>'一个字段的输入短于最小允许长度','There is a field with input that is longer than the maximum allowed length'=>'一个字段输入超过最大允许长度','There is a field that the sender must fill in'=>'发件人必须填写必填项','There are terms that the sender must accept'=>'有些选项发件人必须同意接受','Submission was referred to as spam'=>'提交的邮件被归为垃圾邮件','Validation errors occurred'=>'出现验证错误','Sender\'s message failed to send'=>'发件人的邮件发送失败','Sender\'s message was sent successfully'=>'发件人的邮件已经成功发送','Message Body:'=>'消息正文：','Subject: %s'=>'主题：%s','From: %s'=>'发件人：%s','Send'=>'发送','Your message'=>'您的消息','Your email'=>'您的电邮','Your name'=>'您的名字','Form-tag Generator: %s'=>'Form标签创建：%s','For more information:'=>'想要了解详细情况：','Any information you provide will not be shared with service providers without your authorization.'=>'您所提供的信息未经您同意不会与服务供应商分享。','You may need to first sign up for an account with the service that you plan to use. When you do so, you would need to authorize Contact Form 7 to access the service with your account.'=>'您需要创建帐号以使用服务。创建时，请同时授权Contact Form 7访问您的帐号。','On this screen, you can manage services that are available through Contact Form 7. Using API will allow you to collaborate with any services that are available.'=>'在当前屏幕，您可以管理Contact Form7有关的服务。使用API来进行相关操作。','A mail-tag is also a short code enclosed in square brackets that you can use in every Mail and Mail (2) field. A mail-tag represents a user input value through an input field of a corresponding form-tag.'=>'邮件标签也是置于方括号中的短代码，您可以使用在邮件和邮件 (2) 字段。邮件标签表示用户通过相应的form标签输入字段的输入值。','A form-tag is a short code enclosed in square brackets used in a form content. A form-tag generally represents an input field, and its components can be separated into four parts: type, name, options, and values. Contact Form 7 supports several types of form-tags including text fields, number fields, date fields, checkboxes, radio buttons, menus, file-uploading fields, CAPTCHAs, and quiz fields.'=>'Form标签是在表单内容中的方括号内的简码（short code）。Form标签通常表示一个输入的字段，其组件可以分成四个部分︰ 类型、 名称、 选项和值。Contact Form 7 支持多种类型的表单,包括文本字段、数字字段、日期字段、复选框、单选按钮、菜单、文件上传字段，验证码，和测验字段。','<strong>Additional Settings</strong> provides a place where you can customize the behavior of this contact form by adding code snippets.'=>'<strong>其它设置</strong>提供了使用码段来改变联系表单的方法。','In <strong>Messages</strong>, you can edit various types of messages used for this contact form. These messages are relatively short messages, like a validation error message you see when you leave a required field blank.'=>'在 <strong>邮件信息</strong> 中，您可以编辑各种类型的消息用于此联系表单。这些消息都是相对较短的消息，比如您看到必填的字段为空时的验证错误消息。','<strong>Mail (2)</strong> is an additional mail template that works similar to Mail. Mail (2) is different in that it is sent only when Mail has been sent successfully.'=>'<strong>邮件(2)</strong> 是一个类似于邮件（Mail）的附加的邮件模板。邮件(2) 不同的是它只有当邮件（Mail）已成功发送时发送。','<strong>Mail</strong> manages a mail template (headers and message body) that this contact form will send when users submit it. You can use Contact Form 7&#8217;s mail-tags here.'=>'<strong>邮件</strong> 是一个模板文件（邮件标题和邮件正文），用户提交联系表单时，它将发送该邮件模板。您可以在此使用Contact form 7的邮件标签。','<strong>Form</strong> is a content of HTML form. You can use arbitrary HTML, which is allowed inside a form element. You can also use Contact Form 7&#8217;s form-tags here.'=>'<strong>表单</strong> 是HTML表单的内容。您可以在form元素内使用任意的HTML。您还可以在这里使用Contact Form 7的form标签。','<strong>Title</strong> is the title of a contact form. This title is only used for labeling a contact form, and can be edited.'=>'<strong>标题</strong>是联系表单的标题。标题用于标记该表单，并可进行编辑。','On this screen, you can edit a contact form. A contact form is comprised of the following components:'=>'在该屏幕可以进行联系表单的编辑。联系表单由以下部分组成：','<strong>Duplicate</strong> - Clones that contact form. A cloned contact form inherits all content from the original, but has a different ID.'=>'<strong>复制</strong> -复制表单。复制的表单与原表单内容一致，但ID不同。','<strong>Edit</strong> - Navigates to the editing screen for that contact form. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the contact form title.'=>'<strong>编辑</strong> -打开联系表单编辑屏幕。您也可以单击联系表单进入编辑状态。','Hovering over a row in the contact forms list will display action links that allow you to manage your contact form. You can perform the following actions:'=>'悬停在联系表单中的某一行将显示允许您管理您的联系表单的操作链接。您可以执行以下操作:','On this screen, you can manage contact forms provided by Contact Form 7. You can manage an unlimited number of contact forms. Each contact form has a unique ID and Contact Form 7 shortcode ([contact-form-7 ...]). To insert a contact form into a post or a text widget, insert the shortcode into the target.'=>'在此屏幕上，您可以管理Contact Form7提供的所有表单。您可以管理无限数量的。每个联表单。每一个表单有唯一的ID和Contact Form 7 简码 ([contact-form-7...])。若要在文章或小工具中插入联系表单，只需要输入简码即可。','Mail-tags'=>'Mail标签','Form-tags'=>'表单form标签','Available Actions'=>'可进行的操作','Overview'=>'概述','You can add customization code snippets here. For details, see %s.'=>'您可在此插入自訂代码。详细方式可參考 %s 。','https://contactform7.com/additional-settings/'=>'https://contactform7.com/additional-settings/','File attachments'=>'文件附件','Use HTML content type'=>'使用HTML内容类型','Exclude lines with blank mail-tags from output'=>'不输出空白邮件标签行','Message body'=>'消息正文','Additional headers'=>'附加标题','Subject'=>'主题','From'=>'发件人','To'=>'收件人','In the following fields, you can use these mail-tags:'=>'下面空格中，您可以使用這些邮件标签:','Mail (2) is an additional mail template often used as an autoresponder.'=>'邮箱（2）通常用作自动回复的模板。','Use Mail (2)'=>'使用 Mail (2)','Mail (2)'=>'邮箱（2）','Y/m/d'=>'年/月/日','Edit &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'编辑 &#8220;%s&#8221;','Edit'=>'编辑','Date'=>'日期','Author'=>'作者','Shortcode'=>'简码','Title'=>'标题','Additional Settings'=>'额外的设置','Additional Settings (%d)'=>'附加的设置 (%d)','Messages'=>'留言','Mail'=>'邮箱','Form'=>'表单','Support'=>'支持','https://contactform7.com/support/'=>'https://contactform7.com/support/','FAQ'=>'常见问题解答','https://contactform7.com/faq/'=>'https://contactform7.com/faq/','Docs'=>'文档','https://contactform7.com/docs/'=>'https://contactform7.com/docs/','You are about to delete this contact form.
